
<h2 style="margin-left: 13%;">Task Type</h2>
<style>
    .hoverable:hover {
        background-color: #caccce;
        color: rgb(79, 79, 79);
    }

    div#writing-tab, #reading-tab {
        color: black;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
</style>
<div class="d-flex flex-row flex-wrap text-center m-auto justify-content-evenly p-4 w-75 mb-3">
    <div class="card rounded-pill p-3 mb-3 hoverable" id="writing-tab">
        <div class="card-body">
            <img src="/img/writing.webp" alt="Feature image" class="rounded-circle" width="100px" height="100px" />
            Writing Task
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card rounded-pill p-3 mb-3 hoverable" id="reading-tab">
        <div class="card-body">
            <img src="/img/reading.webp" alt="Feature image" class="rounded-circle" width="100px" height="100px" />
            Reading Task
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="bg-light p-4 w-75 m-auto px-5 d-none" id="writing-div">
    <form action="/writing" method="post">
        <h4>Task 1</h4>
        <p>In Task 1, you are asked to describe some visual information (graph/table/chart/diagram). You need to write 150 words in about 20 minutes.</p>
        <h4>Task 2</h4>
        <p>In Task 2 you are presented with a point of view or argument or problem. You need to write your response in 250 words in about 40 minutes.</p>

        <button class="btn btn-primary my-3">Generate</button>
    </form>
</div>
<div class="bg-light p-4 w-75 m-auto px-5 d-none" id="reading-div">
    <form action="/reading" method="post">
        <h4>Task 1</h4>
        <p>In Task 1, you are asked to describe some visual information (graph/table/chart/diagram). You need to write 150 words in about 20 minutes.</p>

        <button class="btn btn-primary my-3">Generate</button>
    </form>
</div>
<script>
    let selectColor = 'bg-secondary bg-gradient'
    $(document).ready(function () {
        $("#writing-tab").click(function () {
            $(this).addClass(selectColor);
            $('#reading-tab').removeClass(selectColor);
            $('#writing-div').removeClass('d-none');
            $('#reading-div').addClass('d-none');
        });
        $("#reading-tab").click(function () {
            $(this).addClass(selectColor);
            $('#writing-tab').removeClass(selectColor);
            $('#reading-div').removeClass('d-none');
            $('#writing-div').addClass('d-none');
        });
    });
</script>